703763f-a.title: Brooklyn: Columbus Place - Atlantic Avenue
703763f-a.text:
Columbus Place, north of Atlantic Ave., to Herkimer Stroet, showing the
ateeple, rectory and school of St. Benedict's parish. The church faces on
Fulton Street.
April 29, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
